title: Images on the Reame file now shown on a single row
message: Images on the Reame file now shown on a single row

title: - JSON end-point URL changed.
message:
- JSON end-point URL changed.
- buildToolsVersion and targetSdkVersion changed to the last current Android version (6.0 API 23).
- Removed some legacy Apached HTTP Client imports.
- A typo corrected.
- Copyright year updated.

title: Fix for Sony Xperia phones which were not detecting the navigation bar.
message: Fix for Sony Xperia phones which were not detecting the navigation bar.

title: - For HTPP requests AndroidHttpClient has been deprecated. Now using…
message:
- For HTPP requests AndroidHttpClient has been deprecated. Now using HttpURLConnection as stated by Google: https://developer.android.com/preview/behavior-changes.html#behavior-apache-http-client.
- Checkout Activity text rearranged. Lateral margin added to the About text.
- Version code and version number updated.

title: Mocking provider changed from Mockable to Mocky (no Mockable mocks expire after 24h).
message: Mocking provider changed from Mockable to Mocky (no Mockable mocks expire after 24h).

title: Now the app can be installed in the card memory.
message: Now the app can be installed in the card memory.

title: Corrected bug which added extra bottom space to the screen to phones that had…
message: Corrected bug which added extra bottom space to the screen to phones that had physical 'Switch apps' button. These phones (like Samsung Galaxy S5) don't need screen bottom space for the Navigation bar because the phone already has this bar integrated.

title: 'About' text changed and link to GitHub added.
message: 'About' text changed and link to GitHub added.

title: Removed all remaining references to FOODit in both images and texts.
message: Removed all remaining references to FOODit in both images and texts.
